## 4. Swapping the LLM

Default: Anthropic Claude via Claude Code's standard config.

To swap to a different model:

- **OpenAI** — set `CLAUDE_CODE_USE_OPENAI=1` in your environment, drop your key via `./bootstrap-secret {{label}}_openai_api_key sk-...`
- **Local Llama via Ollama** — point Claude Code at `http://localhost:11434/v1/` (OpenAI-compatible endpoint).
- **Bedrock / Vertex** — see Claude Code's docs on model providers.

Each has trade-offs. Anthropic Claude is the most tested with the agent's onboarding flow. Local models work for cost-sensitive installs but onboarding fidelity will be lower.

