## 6. Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Likely cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| Bot not responding | {{provider_label}} plugin failed to start | Check Claude Code session output for plugin errors; `./restart.sh` |
| Agent stuck mid-`/clear` | Cache eviction edge case | Wait 30s, then send a fresh message |
| Heartbeat hasn't fired in 30+ min | `/loop` not re-armed after `/clear` or 7-day expiry | Send "are you /loop-ed?" — agent re-arms |
| Plugin auth expired | OAuth token rotated / revoked | Re-run `./bootstrap-secret {{label}}_*_token <new-value>`; `./restart.sh` |
| Onboarding placeholders still showing | Agent hasn't completed onboarding for that slot | Just answer the questions it asks; it edits the docs incrementally |
| Sensitive data leaked into a draft | Sensitive-data list incomplete | Tell the agent: "add `<thing>` to the sensitive-data list" — it edits `shared/MEMORY.md` |

If something's actually broken, the agent can usually explain its own state via {{provider_label}}. Ask: "what's wrong?"

